prompt: Image Prompt: Create an image depicting a group of people standing in a desolate landscape, with storm clouds overhead and a ray of light shining down on them from the heavens. The people should appear troubled and lost, symbolizing their doomed fate. Include subtle biblical elements such as a distant silhouette of a figure resembling God watching over them, conveying a sense of divine judgement and predestination. Capture the emotional weight and spiritual depth of the concept of God creating doomed individuals.
